changeSet.author: NWM
changeSet.neo4j:cypher: CREATE (n225:node {handle:'case',model:'ICDC',desc:"The Case node contains properties required to unambiguously identify each patient/subject/donor, either based upon the data submitter's original ID, or upon a study-specific Case ID derived from it during data transformation, which prefixes each original ID with a short, study-specific code.",_commit:'2b986a78e01c427e472b06ad1cf2f0a0dfdb7747'})
